Good morning Jamee,



My name is Preeya and I am a construction project manager working with Enbr=
idge on an Integrity repair project in Ontario. The ILI has identified a de=
fect and we are currently discussing with Engineering and Integrity the pos=
sible repair methods. Integrity has suggested one option of using a Type B =
sleeve as a possible repair method. Are you able to provide a quote for a T=
ype B sleeve for our 24=94 pipeline. I can provide other specification as r=
equired, I have not ordered a sleeve in the past so let me know what other =
information you need



We will not be in the position to place an order until Integrity/Engineerin=
g has made a decision on a suitable repair method and vendor but lead time =
and cost is a factor for us to consider. We will likely place the order at =
some point next year (Feb/March/April) if we decide to move forward



Thanks,

Preeya Panchal P. Eng

Sr. Advisor, Construction and Project Management

Engineering Construction

=97

ENBRIDGE

CELL: 647-330-9352

500 Consumers Road, North York,ON, M2J 1P8



enbridge.com<http://www.enbridge.com/>

Safety. Integrity. Respect.






